metadata.description:
The LeaguePass Gold will unlock your access to all current and future LeagueDAO's Web3 fantasy sports leagues hosted on the the LeagueDAO Mega League App.  

Each LeaguePass Gold grants the holder lifetime access to the applicable Fantasy Mega League according to the token properties. 

If you mint a LeaguePass Gold for the Fantasy Football league, you will have FREE access to compete in all future Official LeagueDAO Fantasy Football Mega Leagues. 

Standard LeaguePasses are only good for one season.
metadata.name: LeagueDAO: LeaguePass Gold
